csim5_2_5
Originator: dbailey (David Bailey)
Date: 21 July 2006
Model: CSIM
Version: 5.2.5
One-line Summary: Changed module for sys_shr_flush
CCSM Version compatible with:
Changes made:

- shr_shr_flush should be found in sys_shr_mod

M /csim4/trunk/models/ice/csim4/source/ice.F
